◘ sum(·) — 합계
◘ ════════════════════════
˙ ·∘∘∘
˙∘ ·
⋮
  ◘ total = 0, i = 0
  ••
  ∘⋅ ·∘
  ••
  ∘⋅ ··
  ‥‥
  ⋮
    ∘∘ ··
    ∘∘ ·
    ⸳‧
    ⋅‧‧‧
  ⋮⋮
  ⋮
