◘ reverse(·) — 역순 복사본
◘ ════════════════════════
˙ ·∘·∘
˙∘ ·
⋮
  ◘ i = len(arr)-1
  ∘∘ ·
  ⸳‧
  •·•
  ⋅⋅
  ∘⋅ ·∘
  ◘ result = []
  ••
  ◦
  ∘⋅ ··
  ‥‥
  ⋮
    ◘ cond: i >= 0
    ∘∘ ·∘
    ••
    ⋅‧∘∘∘
  ⋮⋮
  ⋮
    ∘∘ ··
    ∘∘ ·
    ∘∘ ·∘
    ◦◦
    ◦∘
    ∘⋅ ··
    ∘∘ ·∘
    •·•
    ⋅⋅
    ∘⋅ ·∘
